i-provider&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;This position&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;provides&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;an opportunity to take on a role in an entrepreneurial culture and gain a broad perspective across the insurance business. As a member of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;either&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;Commercial&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;Actuarial&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;team, you will be asked to assist in providing technical and analytical assessments of complex business issues related to the development of new property products and maintenance of existing ones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;utiliz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;ing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;ui-provider&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;actuarial techniques to assist in the development and maintenance of sophisticated pricing plans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233279&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contra

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re looking for the stability of a profitable, growing company with the entrepreneurial spirit of a startup, we’re hiring. &lt;strong&gt;SageSure&lt;/strong&gt;, a leader in catastrophe-exposed property insurance, is seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Assistant Vice President (AVP) of Total Rewards&lt;/strong&gt;. This role is ideal for a seasoned Total Rewards leader with &lt;strong&gt;private equity experience&lt;/strong&gt;, strong operational rigor, and the executive presence to partner effectively across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the AVP, Total Rewards, you will &lt;strong&gt;own both the strategy and execution&lt;/strong&gt; of SageSure’s Total Rewards roadmap—shaping compensation, benefits, equity, payroll, and HR systems to attract, retain, and motivate a geographically distributed workforce. This role is &lt;strong&gt;equally tactical and strategic&lt;/strong&gt;, requiring deep hands-on expertise alongside the ability to influence senior leaders and guide change at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will play a critical role in ensuring our programs are compliant, competitive, scalable, and aligned with the expectations of a &lt;strong&gt;private equity–backed environment&lt;/strong&gt;, while leading and developing a high-performing &lt;strong&gt;remote team&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Non-Negotiables&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Private Equity–Backed Company Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Direct experience operating within a private equity–backed organization, including administering and evolving Total Rewards programs in a PE environment with strong governance, pace, and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Equity &amp;amp; NSO Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hands-on experience designing, administering, and educating stakeholders on equity programs, including Non-Stock Options (NSOs) and other private-company equity vehicles, with a strong understanding of tax and compliance implications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operationally Strong Total Rewards Leader&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Demonstrated ability to operate at both a strategic and highly tactical level, with deep ownership of day-to-day execution across compensation, benefits, equity, payroll, and HR systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remote Workforce Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Proven success leading and developing a remote or highly distributed team, with the ability to drive accountability, performance, and engagement across geographies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multi-State Workforce &amp;amp; Payroll Tax Mastery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Deep experience managing a workforce across 45 states, with expert-level knowledge of payroll tax nuances, compliance requirements, and risk mitigation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HRIS Transformation Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Demonstrated success &lt;strong&gt;r&lt;/strong&gt;eplacing, significantly upgrading, or optimizing legacy HRIS and People systems to support scale, reporting, compliance, and improved employee experience in a growing organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audit &amp;amp; Compliance Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Strong background in auditing compensation, benefits, equity, and payroll practices, with a rigorous focus on compliance, internal controls, and regulatory adherence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Change Management Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Proven ability to lead and execute enterprise-level change, including systems implementations, program redesigns, and process improvements, while effectively influencing stakeholders at all levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Presence &amp;amp; Leadership Partnership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Clear executive presence with the ability to serve as a trusted partner

