&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SageSure&amp;nbsp;is seeking a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager, People&amp;nbsp;Analytics&amp;nbsp;and Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to build and scale a modern analytics capability within the People function.&amp;nbsp;This role reports to the Director, People&amp;nbsp;Strategy&amp;nbsp;and Operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is responsible for establishing foundational reporting, defining key workforce metrics, and delivering insights that inform strategic decision-making for our business leaders. You will operate as a hands-on builder, creating structure from fragmented data and evolving capabilities over time, including increased automation and more advanced approaches where sensible (e.g., AI-enabled analytics).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will partner closely with People leadership, People Systems, FP&amp;amp;A, and Corporate IT to ensure data is accurate, accessible, and effectively used to drive decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
